{"tid":1396403,"cid":36,"subCid":0,"title":"急性壓力疾患 (Acute stress disorder)","createTime":"2019-08-02T05:42:29.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-04T20:20:14.000Z","uid":261084,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"fcf883825e886c2c8f10be344a1f3833bb5fa9a6","tid":1396403,"uid":261084,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-02T05:42:29.000Z","msg":"三分鐘秒懂心理學 急性壓力疾患 (Acute stress disorder)<br />\n<br />\n最近無論你是看電視或是看平板手機📱<br />\n打開節目你一定會經驗到、目擊<br />\n或被迫面對到一或多種事件<br />\n此人的反應包括<br />\n強烈的害怕😨 無助感 😔 或恐怖感😱<br />\n<br />\n如是這樣請小心留意自己的心理狀態🧐<br />\n因為急性壓力疾患(Acute stress disorder) <br />\n可能已籠罩到你身上<br />\n<br />\n愈是直接接觸創傷事件的人<br />\n所承受的心理壓力就會越高😵<br />\n即使只是間接目睹亦可能造成創傷<br />\n經常觀看媒體報道的衝擊畫面<br />\n也有可能出現情緒困擾🤢<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/gLYU0J6HLgs\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FgLYU0J6HLgs&d=7fFLqiM2ByXH61viL1oyjIeonPPUtn1HApnj2AcFxYA%3D&h=0bae56bd\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/gLYU0J6HLgs</a>"},{"pid":"1e0e7c49b353c70b8f9db5f60401597e32dd2bd8","tid":1396403,"uid":293841,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-02T11:00:45.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong>【和理非入】輔導員獻計：如何與同路人同行？<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1395084\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1395084</a></strong></span>"},{"pid":"47d0ba083d2a24cc91470c383f966648a0c009f1","tid":1396403,"uid":261084,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"1e0e7c49b353c70b8f9db5f60401597e32dd2bd8","tid":1396403,"uid":293841,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-02T11:00:45.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong>【和理非入】輔導員獻計：如何與同路人同行？<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1395084\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1395084</a></strong></span>"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-02T18:36:50.000Z","msg":"樓主有文字版我就出返個視像版 有好的心理質數先可以面對困境<br />\n<br />\n三分鐘秒懂心理學---安慰別人三大法寶: 積極聆聽、 眼神制敵、 寶礦力<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtu